  "body": "```html\r\n<scroller style=\"position:relative;background-color:#f0f0f0;\">\r\n    <refresh style=\"width:750;flex-direction:row;justify-content:center;align-items:center;\" display=\"{{refreshDisplay}}\" onpullingdown='onpullingdown' onrefresh=\"onrefresh\">\r\n        <loading-indicator style=\"height:80;width:80;color:#ff6700\" if=\"{{refreshDisplay=='show'}}\"></loading-indicator>\r\n        <text class=\"refresh-arrow\" if=\"{{refreshDisplay=='hide'}}\">下拉刷新</text>\r\n    </refresh>\r\n    <div style=\"position:fixed;top:0;left:0;background-color:#000;width:750px;height:88px;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"height:2000px\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;background-color:#000;width:750px;height:100px;\"></div>\r\n  </scroller>\r\n```\r\n\r\n用安卓playground打开[上述代码运行结果](http://dotwe.org/d03f0912d2af73db2cfb32d1cbed0504)\r\n\r\n如果给refresh高度，则设top为refresh高度才能定位准确，bottom为-refresh高度定位准确。",
